---
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';

const title = 'Tibia Damage Calculator - Melee, Distance & Magic Damage';
const description = 'Calculate your damage output in Tibia. Melee damage for Knights, distance damage for Paladins, and spell damage for Sorcerers and Druids.';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={title} description={description} />
		<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
			"@context": "https://schema.org",
			"@type": "WebApplication",
			"name": "Tibia Damage Calculator",
			"description": description,
			"url": "https://tibiamobile.com/tools/damage-calculator",
			"applicationCategory": "GameApplication",
			"operatingSystem": "Any",
			"offers": {
				"@type": "Offer",
				"price": "0",
				"priceCurrency": "USD"
			}
		})} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
				<a href="/tools">Tools</a> <span class="sep">/</span> <span>Damage Calculator</span>
			</nav>

			<h1>Tibia Damage Calculator</h1>
			<p class="intro">Calculate your average damage output per turn. Select your vocation and enter your stats to see minimum, maximum, and average damage.</p>

			<section class="calculator card">
				<div class="calc-inputs">
					<div class="input-group">
						<label for="vocation">Vocation</label>
						<select id="vocation">
							<option value="knight">Knight</option>
							<option value="paladin">Paladin</option>
							<option value="sorcerer">Sorcerer</option>
							<option value="druid">Druid</option>
						</select>
					</div>
					<div class="input-group">
						<label for="char-level">Level</label>
						<input type="number" id="char-level" min="1" max="10000" value="50" />
					</div>
					<div class="input-group">
						<label for="skill-level" id="skill-label">Skill Level (Sword)</label>
						<input type="number" id="skill-level" min="0" max="200" value="50" />
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="calc-inputs" style="margin-top: 1em;">
					<div class="input-group" id="skill-type-group">
						<label for="skill-type">Weapon Skill</label>
						<select id="skill-type">
							<option value="sword">Sword</option>
							<option value="axe">Axe</option>
							<option value="club">Club</option>
						</select>
					</div>
					<div class="input-group" id="attack-group">
						<label for="weapon-attack">Weapon Attack</label>
						<input type="number" id="weapon-attack" min="0" max="100" value="35" />
					</div>
					<button id="calc-btn" class="calc-button">Calculate</button>
				</div>

				<div id="calc-results" class="calc-results" style="display:none;">
					<div class="result-cards">
						<div class="result-card">
							<span class="result-label">Min Damage</span>
							<span class="result-value" id="dmg-min">--</span>
						</div>
						<div class="result-card">
							<span class="result-label">Max Damage</span>
							<span class="result-value" id="dmg-max">--</span>
						</div>
						<div class="result-card">
							<span class="result-label">Average Damage</span>
							<span class="result-value" id="dmg-avg">--</span>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div id="formula-note" class="formula-note"></div>
				</div>

				<p id="calc-error" class="calc-error" style="display:none;"></p>
			</section>

			<section class="reference-section">
				<h2>Tibia Damage Formulas</h2>
				<p>The damage you deal in Tibia depends on your vocation, level, relevant skill, and weapon attack value. Below are the formulas used for each combat type.</p>

				<h3>Melee Damage (Knights)</h3>
				<p>Knights deal physical damage based on their melee skill (sword, axe, or club) and weapon attack:</p>
				<code class="formula-block">Damage = 0 to (0.085 * Attack * Skill + 0.085 * Level * Attack / 20)</code>
				<p>Each hit is randomly distributed between 0 and the maximum. On average, you will deal about half the maximum damage per turn.</p>

				<h3>Distance Damage (Paladins)</h3>
				<p>Paladins use distance fighting and benefit from a slightly higher damage modifier:</p>
				<code class="formula-block">Damage = 0 to (0.09 * Attack * Skill + 0.09 * Level * Attack / 20)</code>
				<p>Distance attacks follow the same random distribution, dealing between 0 and the maximum on each shot.</p>

				<h3>Magic Damage (Sorcerers & Druids)</h3>
				<p>Spell damage for basic strike spells (like Exori Vis, Exori Flam, etc.) scales with your level and magic level:</p>
				<code class="formula-block">Damage = Level * 0.2 + Magic Level * 3</code>
				<p>This is an approximate formula for basic strike spells. Actual damage varies by spell and can be affected by equipment bonuses.</p>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<script>
	var vocationEl = document.getElementById('vocation');
	var levelEl = document.getElementById('char-level');
	var skillEl = document.getElementById('skill-level');
	var skillLabelEl = document.getElementById('skill-label');
	var skillTypeGroup = document.getElementById('skill-type-group');
	var skillTypeEl = document.getElementById('skill-type');
	var attackGroup = document.getElementById('attack-group');
	var attackEl = document.getElementById('weapon-attack');
	var resultsEl = document.getElementById('calc-results');
	var errorEl = document.getElementById('calc-error');

	function updateUI() {
		var vocation = vocationEl.value;
		if (vocation === 'knight') {
			skillTypeGroup.style.display = '';
			attackGroup.style.display = '';
			skillTypeEl.innerHTML = '<option value="sword">Sword</option><option value="axe">Axe</option><option value="club">Club</option>';
			skillLabelEl.textContent = 'Skill Level (' + skillTypeEl.options[skillTypeEl.selectedIndex].text + ')';
		} else if (vocation === 'paladin') {
			skillTypeGroup.style.display = 'none';
			attackGroup.style.display = '';
			skillLabelEl.textContent = 'Distance Fighting';
		} else {
			skillTypeGroup.style.display = 'none';
			attackGroup.style.display = 'none';
			skillLabelEl.textContent = 'Magic Level';
		}
	}

	function calculate() {
		var vocation = vocationEl.value;
		var level = parseInt(levelEl.value, 10);
		var skill = parseInt(skillEl.value, 10);
		var attack = parseInt(attackEl.value, 10);

		errorEl.style.display = 'none';
		resultsEl.style.display = 'none';

		if (isNaN(level) || level < 1) {
			errorEl.textContent = 'Please enter a valid level (1 or higher).';
			errorEl.style.display = 'block';
			return;
		}
		if (isNaN(skill) || skill < 0) {
			errorEl.textContent = 'Please enter a valid skill level (0 or higher).';
			errorEl.style.display = 'block';
			return;
		}

		var minDmg = 0;
		var maxDmg = 0;
		var formulaText = '';

		if (vocation === 'knight') {
			if (isNaN(attack) || attack < 1) {
				errorEl.textContent = 'Please enter a valid weapon attack value (1 or higher).';
				errorEl.style.display = 'block';
				return;
			}
			maxDmg = 0.085 * attack * skill + 0.085 * level * attack / 20;
			formulaText = 'Melee: 0 to (0.085 * ' + attack + ' * ' + skill + ' + 0.085 * ' + level + ' * ' + attack + ' / 20) = ' + Math.floor(maxDmg);
		} else if (vocation === 'paladin') {
			if (isNaN(attack) || attack < 1) {
				errorEl.textContent = 'Please enter a valid weapon attack value (1 or higher).';
				errorEl.style.display = 'block';
				return;
			}
			maxDmg = 0.09 * attack * skill + 0.09 * level * attack / 20;
			formulaText = 'Distance: 0 to (0.09 * ' + attack + ' * ' + skill + ' + 0.09 * ' + level + ' * ' + attack + ' / 20) = ' + Math.floor(maxDmg);
		} else {
			maxDmg = level * 0.2 + skill * 3;
			formulaText = 'Magic: ' + level + ' * 0.2 + ' + skill + ' * 3 = ' + Math.floor(maxDmg);
		}

		maxDmg = Math.floor(maxDmg);
		var avgDmg = Math.floor((minDmg + maxDmg) / 2);

		document.getElementById('dmg-min').textContent = minDmg;
		document.getElementById('dmg-max').textContent = maxDmg;
		document.getElementById('dmg-avg').textContent = avgDmg;
		document.getElementById('formula-note').textContent = formulaText;

		resultsEl.style.display = 'block';
	}

	vocationEl.addEventListener('change', function() {
		updateUI();
		calculate();
	});

	skillTypeEl.addEventListener('change', function() {
		skillLabelEl.textContent = 'Skill Level (' + skillTypeEl.options[skillTypeEl.selectedIndex].text + ')';
	});

	document.getElementById('calc-btn').addEventListener('click', calculate);

	levelEl.addEventListener('keydown', function(e) {
		if (e.key === 'Enter') calculate();
	});
	skillEl.addEventListener('keydown', function(e) {
		if (e.key === 'Enter') calculate();
	});
	attackEl.addEventListener('keydown', function(e) {
		if (e.key === 'Enter') calculate();
	});

	updateUI();
	calculate();
</script>

<style>
	.breadcrumb {
		font-size: 0.85em;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		margin-bottom: 1.5em;
	}
	.breadcrumb a {
		color: var(--accent);
	}
	.breadcrumb .sep {
		margin: 0 0.4em;
		color: var(--border);
	}
	.intro {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 1.05em;
		margin-bottom: 2em;
	}
	.calculator {
		margin-bottom: 3em;
	}
	.calc-inputs {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1em;
		align-items: flex-end;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}
	.input-group {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.35em;
		flex: 1;
		min-width: 120px;
	}
	.input-group label {
		font-size: 0.85em;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-weight: 700;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.03em;
	}
	.input-group input,
	.input-group select {
		padding: 0.6em 0.8em;
		background: var(--bg-dark);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: 6px;
		color: var(--text-heading);
		font-size: 1.1em;
		font-family: inherit;
		width: 100%;
	}
	.input-group input:focus,
	.input-group select:focus {
		outline: none;
		border-color: var(--accent);
		box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(200, 168, 78, 0.2);
	}
	.input-group select option {
		background: var(--bg-dark);
		color: var(--text-heading);
	}
	.calc-button {
		padding: 0.65em 1.8em;
		background: var(--accent);
		color: var(--bg-dark);
		border: none;
		border-radius: 6px;
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 1em;
		font-family: inherit;
		cursor: pointer;
		transition: background 0.2s;
		white-space: nowrap;
	}
	.calc-button:hover {
		background: var(--accent-light);
	}
	.calc-error {
		color: #e05555;
		margin-top: 1em;
		font-size: 0.95em;
	}
	.calc-results {
		margin-top: 1.5em;
	}
	.result-cards {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 1em;
		margin-bottom: 1em;
	}
	.result-card {
		background: var(--bg-dark);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: 8px;
		padding: 1em;
		text-align: center;
	}
	.result-label {
		display: block;
		font-size: 0.8em;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.03em;
		margin-bottom: 0.4em;
	}
	.result-value {
		display: block;
		font-size: 1.3em;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--accent);
	}
	.formula-note {
		font-size: 0.85em;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		background: var(--bg-dark);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: 6px;
		padding: 0.75em 1em;
		font-family: monospace;
	}

	/* Reference section */
	.reference-section {
		margin-top: 3em;
	}
	.reference-section h2 {
		color: var(--accent);
		margin-bottom: 0.5em;
	}
	.reference-section h3 {
		font-size: 1.15em;
		margin-top: 1.5em;
		margin-bottom: 0.4em;
	}
	.reference-section > p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		margin-bottom: 1em;
	}
	.reference-section p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 0.95em;
	}
	.formula-block {
		display: block;
		padding: 0.75em 1em;
		margin-bottom: 1em;
		font-size: 0.9em;
		background: var(--bg-card);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: 6px;
	}

	@media (max-width: 720px) {
		.calc-inputs {
			flex-direction: column;
		}
		.result-cards {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
		.result-value {
			font-size: 1.15em;
		}
	}
</style>
